    Streampusher 2 is NOT affiliated with <a href="https://shrimpshake.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Shirmp Shake Co. LTD</a>, or any Shrimp Shake related products. In fact we don't even like the stuff, <strong>yuck!</strong> If you receive any emails from Shrimp Shake Co asking to reset your datafruits or streampusher password do NOT respond do not even look at the message, throw your computer away as quickly as possible and buy a new one.
  </div>
</section>
